    landingWeekDesc: "A realistic weekly training plan generated by Sportstalent for a competitive sparring athlete in the preparation phase. This plan integrates with 3 weekly TKD sessions and includes sport-specific strength work designed for kick power and competition readiness.",
    landingPhase: "Phase",
