    aboutHeroDesc: "We bring sport science-based strength & conditioning to every taekwondo athlete — from white belts to world champions.",
    aboutMissionTitle: "Our Mission",
    aboutMissionDesc: "To democratize access to periodized, evidence-based training programs that were previously only available to national team athletes. Every taekwondo practitioner deserves a program built on real sport science.",
    aboutVisionTitle: "Our Vision",
    aboutVisionDesc: "A world where every martial artist trains smarter — where injuries are prevented, performance is measured, and progress is visible. Technology should serve the athlete, not replace the coach.",
    aboutTeamTitle: "Our Team",
    aboutTeamDesc: "Sportstalent is built by coaches, sport scientists, and taekwondo athletes who understand the unique demands of the sport. We combine decades of mat experience with modern training science.",

